column5: Shes a good fisherman and just starting Walleye fishing but shes doing pretty well. This time of year in Kansas we're only fishing 7' deep. I laughed my butt off but her language is a little strong.
That was great, mesmerizing in fact.
Very entertaining! A future fishing show career perhaps?

Someone's taught her well. Good job Mopar. Must be nice to have good strong young teeth. Buy the kid a line cutter, I cringed every time I watched her bite off the line. That line looked pretty heavy for Pickerel. I have never seen a flathead, very interesting, looks like a white Pic with dark spots. Do they taste similar to Walleye Mopar?
She's got no fear of fish at all...I'd show this to my wife, but I doubt she'll take away the right message.
I had visions of a booby fish in the middle of the screen..she has potential for a real fishing girl show.
A flathead is a type of catfish.
That's kind of you guys, thanks. She just lives to fish and she's been making these crazy videos. Awesome kid.
Simply outstanding.. The raw emotion was refreshing..   The first time I swore in front of my Dad was when I was 10 and I meant every word.. It was over a fish that broke my line.
10:08 to the end is just priceless.  Awesome video of a pretty girl who loves fishing... future in TV fishing shows?  Thanks for the share

I understand entirely  I believe that her goal  She is (gulp) somewhat raw. Glad you understand her  I show this to her. Thanks  She insists on coming with me to Canada next summer. It would be my joy if she met a Canadian young man.  HaHa I rewatched it and agree!
you should be proud! I lol'd multiple times.  Go Chiefs! My aunt and uncle live in Olathe, been to a few games.
That was a great video !!!! Thanks for sharing .. She loves fishing that's for sure!!!! Cheers
Awesome daughter you have!  I thoroughly enjoyed the video!  I like the green tape on her wound.
That was awesome..   I would have loved to see what she would have done if she'd got that big one up to the kayak!!! --  Someone send that girl some fireline or powerpro!!
